::Teltoli SilverWing::

Opening her eyes again, Teltoli looked down and saw they were high 
up, and from the position he was in, she could tell he was about to 
dive. And all that was between them and Maximal Ship was.. the 
shield. She opened her comlink and spoke to the Maximal base.

:::Please, you really need to open the sheild, now, or we're gonna be 
scarp!::: She pleaded, a small tremble in her voice. Teltoli may be 
an adult, but with practially the whole Alliance out for her blood, 
she didn't really feel like one!
